  • Whether there are known timeout, heartbeat, or IP-change sensitivity issues when integrated with OpenPhone

  • Whether any recent Mojo updates could be causing forced session resets

Please advise what logs, timestamps, or diagnostic steps you need from us to identify the root cause.

This issue is significantly disrupting live outbound calling, so we need to isolate and resolve it as soon as possible.
